1.title: Good Girls Don't Make History
1.plot: On the Season 8 premiere of Total Divas, Nicole, Brie, Trinity, Paige, Nattie, Nia and Lana take over New Orleans for an epic WrestleMania with a historic number of women's matches. Nia prepares for the match of her lifetime, a championship match at WrestleMania, while Paige takes the women on a wild tour to explore all that New Orleans has to offer while struggling to find her identity in WWE after her potentially career-ending injury. Meanwhile, Nattie promises the Bella Army an appearance that the Bella Twins did not agree to and has to suffer the consequences.

2.title: This Is My House
2.plot: The Bellas support and watch Trinity, Nattie and Lana compete in the Women's Battle Royal, and Nia's anxiety goes into overdrive before her match. Meanwhile, Paige comes to terms with her retirement and seeks advice from Daniel Bryan.

1.title: Welcome to the WWE
1.plot: The WWE Divas begin their preparations for WrestleMania XXIX. Nikki starts to have doubts regarding her relationship with John. Trinity is embarrassed when Ariane's boyfriend Vincent ends up causing a scene backstage and she's stuck in the middle.

2.title: A Tango with Fandango
2.plot: Diva-in-training Eva Marie tries to fast-track her way up the WWE ladder; the Bella Twins vacation with John Cena and Daniel Bryan; Trinity and Ariane deal with a wardrobe malfunction.

3.title: Planet Funk Is Funked Up
3.plot: Trinity faces John Uso in the ring just as they are on the verge of calling their relationship quits; at the same time, Nikki doesn't react well to news that Brie wants to move to Phoenix; and JoJo is given an ultimatum by her boyfriend.

4.title: The Fat Twin
4.plot: Nikki worries about her weight after Brie and social media suggest that she's fat. Meanwhile, Ariane thinks about getting breast implants; and Natalya wishes her fiancé would be more romantic.

5.title: Feuding Funkadactyls
5.plot: The feuding between Trinity and Ariane threatens to get them both fired; Nikki meets up with her estranged father; and a friend confesses he wants to be more than that with Nattie.

6.title: Diva Las Vegas
6.plot: The WWE Divas and Superstars attend a bachelorette party in Las Vegas for Nattie; at the same time, JoJo is warned by her friends about dating the much older Justin Gabriel; and Ariane grows angry at her boyfriend after he loses his temper in front of her coworkers.

7.title: A Leg Up
7.plot: Nikki could be sidelined by an old leg injury; at the same time, Eva Marie gets a spread in Maxim magazine; Ariane becomes nervous when Vinnie starts talking marriage; and JoJo has a hard time finding her voice.

8.title: No Longer the Bridesmaid
8.plot: Nattie's dream wedding doesn't go off as planned; Nikki is invited to meet John Cena's family; Ariane deals with a medical emergency; and one of the newcomers makes her WWE debut.

9.title: Summerslam
9.plot: Eva Marie's rising popularity is seen as a threat by Nikki; Ariane works on anger management; and an accident during a match leaves Nattie worried about returning to the ring for SummerSlam.

10.title: Nurse Nikki
10.plot: Nikki moves in with John Cena and he shocks her with an unexpected demand; at the same time, Eva Marie considers cheating after she's asked to announce on live TV.

11.title: Seeing Red
11.plot: Nattie has a feeling that Eva Marie is trying to cozy up to her man; Nikki wonders if she can accept John Cena's demand; and Brie has issues with Bryan's increasing fame.

12.title: Get That Chingle Chingle
12.plot: Ariane pushes Vincent to try out for the WWE; John Cena's house doesn't quite feel like home yet to Nikki; and Trinity's relationship with Jon is affected when her dad arrives for an extended stay.

13.title: Saying Goodbye
13.plot: Nattie and TJ are forced to say goodbye to a beloved pet; Trinity has it out with Jon over his jealous behavior; and Nikki's medical leave causes tensions between herself and Brie.

14.title: Ready to Ride
14.plot: In the Season 1 finale, Bryan pops the question to Brie in a romantic setting; at the same time, Nikki feels uncertain about her future with John Cena after a heated discussion about marriage and children; and the first meeting between Eva Marie's fiancé and her family goes horribly wrong.

16.title: The Reunion After Party Show
16.plot: The stars of Total Divas reunite to discuss the highs and lows of tonight's episode with special guest, John Cena.

1.title: New Diva on the Block
1.plot: Nikki faces life without her boyfriend, John Cena. Summer Rae joins the main roster and Eva Marie faces her parents after they find out about her elopement.

2.title: The Braniel Bus
2.plot: Brie convinces Bryan to get a tour bus; Eva Marie is embarrassed when her past is exposed, and Nikki loses a tooth in a match.

3.title: On Brie's Bad Side
3.plot: When Summer Rae flirts with Bryan, she makes an instant enemy of Brie; Nattie continues to feud with Summer Rae.

4.title: Inhale, Exhale
4.plot: Nattie faces surgery after a nasal injury; Nikki suspects John Cena of cheating, and Trinity makes a music video.

5.title: For Better or for Worse
5.plot: Trinity wants to get married, but not without Jon's father's blessing; Eva faces a serious health issue, while Nikki and Ariane help Nattie get her groove back.

6.title: The House Sitters
6.plot: Ariane throws a party while house sitting for Nattie and loses her cat. Nattie and T.J. clash over money while vacationing in New York City, and Brie terrorizes Nikki about the food she eats.

7.title: Flirting with Fandango
7.plot: Summer Rae takes her relationship with Fandango to the next level; Brie can't enjoy being a bride, and Trinity betrays Jon behind his back.

8.title: Red and Gold
8.plot: Eva Marie and Summer Rae battle outside the ring after being paired together in the ring; Ariane takes it too far when trying to become famous and Nattie shows her artistic side.

9.title: What Happens in Cabo
9.plot: While at Brie's bachelorette party in Mexico, Eva Marie struggles with her sobriety, Nikki reveals a secret from her past; Trinity suffers a serious eye injury.

10.title: Digging a Hole
10.plot: The Bella sisters clash as Brie's wedding fast approaches and Nikki avoids telling John about her previous marriage. Meanwhile, the Divas find out who will be competing at WrestleMania.

11.title: Wedding Mania
11.plot: Brie and Bryan get married, Nikki's secret marriage is finally exposed to John and the Divas compete at WrestleMania for the Diva's Championship.

1.title: Eggs Over Freezing
1.plot: Season three kicks off with Nikki planning for a future without current boyfriend John Cena. Meanwhile, Eva's life is turned upside down when she must decide between family and her husband. And tensions are high when a former diva returns to the roster, and later reveals a dark secret.

2.title: Mo' Marriage, Mo' Problems
2.plot: Brie regrets quarreling with her husband when he delivers devastating news; Nikki's secret has John fearing the end of their relationship, and Trinity is blindsided when Ariane puts the future of the Funkadactyls at risk.

3.title: Roadside Rumble
3.plot: Brie and Bryan's wrestling careers are in jeopardy, and Brie's attempt to save their future puts Nikki in a tough spot with John. Meanwhile, Rosa fails miserably at reconciling two enemies, and the wedding standoff between Eva's father and husband comes to a head.

4.title: Divas Unchained
4.plot: With Nattie taking a break from TJ, she is hit on by an unexpected colleague. Meanwhile, Trinity's inability to have sex frustrates Jon, and Bryan & Nikki shock Brie when they team up to stage an intervention.

5.title: Scared Straight
5.plot: Brie is left helpless when Bryan's injury takes a turn for the worst. Meanwhile, Ariane's mother calls with a desperate plea for help, and Eva is shocked when Jonathan makes a dangerous decision without her consent.

6.title: Paint the Island Red
6.plot: Eva's sexy bachelorette in Curacao gets heated when TJ destroys Nattie's hopes of rekindling their marriage, Nikki believes she's lost her twin sister, and Ariane kicks Vinnie's desires to the curb.

7.title: The Double-Cross
7.plot: Nikki is devastated when she discovers John's kept a secret from her. Meanwhile, Rosa's unaware she's competing in her pursuits of an NFL player, and Nattie's unsavory comments to a reporter cause TJ to take an extreme action.

8.title: Cross Country Catastrophe
8.plot: Things spiral out of control when Rosa discovers Summer with her man. Meanwhile, what starts as a couples road trip for Eva and Ariane ends in an all out blowout, and Brie is thrown for a loop when she finds out Bryan is keeping tabs on her.

9.title: Daddy's Little Girl
9.plot: Eva lashes out at Jonathan and Brie as she comes to terms with her Dad's terminal cancer. Ariane's plan to hire Nikki as her real estate agent backfires, and Nattie and TJ face the harsh realities of getting a divorce.

10.title: The Divas Are Taking Over
10.plot: Amidst Eva's wedding day, Brie confronts John behind Nikki's back leading to explosive consequences, and Nattie's caught in a downward spiral when the truth about her marriage is revealed to the divas.

11.title: Her Highness
11.plot: The Bella family erupts when Nikki learns the truth about John. Meanwhile, a member of UK wrestling royalty, Paige, takes the Divas division by storm and Nattie takes desperate measures to avoid getting caught in an illegal act.

11.title: The Draft
11.plot: Nikki starts practicing in the performance center, meanwhile the girls start worrying about the brand extension. Paige and Lana lost it after being drafted away from the loved ones.

12.title: Feel the Glow
12.plot: Naomi is nervous about her new entrance. Eva and Maryse plan a Baywatch themed photo-shoot.

13.title: Group-Sext
13.plot: Maryse takes her eyes problems serious after accidentally sending hot photos to a group chat. On a charity trip, Lana spends more time with Rusev than with her friends.

14.title: Runaway Bride
14.plot: Lana doesn't want to follow Rusev's Bulgarian's's wedding traditions. Eva Marie worries about her dad health.

15.title: Swimming with Pigs
15.plot: Nikki works on her new finisher move. Maryse and Miz (with Eva) go on a delayed-honey moon. She wants to have intimate honey moon moments but Mike has his mind else were.

16.title: Total Summerslam
16.plot: Maryse has her prom and Nikki comes back for Summerslam.

1.title: This Is Make or Break
1.plot: The WWE announces its first ever Money in the Bank ladder match for the women's superstar division; Nikki mentors Nattie and Lana in hopes of becoming Smackdown GM; Nia Jax makes a bad impression when she questions Maryse's WWE history.

2.title: Dressed Like a Champ
2.plot: The ladies celebrate the success of their historic ladder match, but Lana's performance suffers intense scrutiny; Maryse's fashion makeover triggers Alexa's painful past; Nattie, who hates babies, is tasked to babysit Brie's newborn.

3.title: Breaking All the Rules
3.plot: Trinity goes behind WWE's back and alters her championship in order to give it a glow; Lana pulls a stunt that could get her fired; Brie recruits Nikki to go on a road trip to San Diego with a breastfeeding infant in the car.

4.title: The Diva Divide
4.plot: A fight breaks out between Lana, Nattie and Nia when their critique of each other's wrestling skills becomes too personal; a third home robbery makes Maryse want to move; Brie begins donating her breast milk to babies in need.

5.title: Bella Rush
5.plot: Lana hosts a Bulgarian Name's Day party for Rusev in Nashville but isn't ready to give him what he really wants as a present; Nattie buys her parents a house, but soon realizes they are the tenants from hell.

6.title: Divas Gone Wild
6.plot: Brie struggles to enjoy herself on her first vacation away from her newborn, but Brie Mode eventually makes a return; the tension between Nattie and Lana reaches a climax and threatens to ruin everyone's time.

7.title: Fake It 'Til You Make It
7.plot: After surviving her first trip away from Birdie, Brie becomes inspired to make a comeback in the ring; Trin introduces role-playing in the bedroom; Maryse dares Mike to be a vegetarian for a week.

8.title: Single in the City
8.plot: Nia confronts Alexa on her sketchy wedding plans and ruins the fun; Lana's physical affection for women pushes Rusev to his limit as a husband; Carmella confronts Lana for messing with her career.

9.title: Three Alarm Fire
9.plot: Nia faces her fears and braves a date with a NYC firefighter; Lana's criticism of Nattie's skills on the mic gets in Nattie's head before her big SummerSlam match, forcing Nattie to do something drastic.
